'''Steve Williams''', an [[Industrial Light & Magic|ILM]] animator, was an uncredited extra in the [[The Star Wars Trilogy Special Edition|Special Edition]] of [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']]. He portrayed an individual walking into the [[Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina|cantina]] in [[Mos Eisley]], wearing a [[Weequay]] vest that was used in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']].<ref name="Wretched Hive" />

